    HasLaw (fun ω ↦ @Bandits.ArrayModel.hist α R mα mR inst✝⁶ inst✝⁵ inst✝⁴ alg (ω.1) n) (fun i ↦ ν ((fun x ↦ x.1) (fun _ ↦ (initAlgFunction alg i, (ν i) (initAlgFunction alg i)))) := by
